<MainLayout title="How I Use The Edison Wave in My Morning Routine for Maximum Productivity" description="Learn how to integrate brainwave entrainment into your daily routine. A step-by-step guide to using The Edison Wave for enhanced focus and productivity.">

<article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
  <header class="mb-12">
    <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
      <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 text-sm font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Tips</span>
      <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm ml-4">January 10, 2025</span>
      <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm ml-4">6 min read</span>
    </div>
    
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
      How I Use The Edison Wave in My Morning Routine for Maximum Productivity
    </h1>
    
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
      Learn how to integrate brainwave entrainment into your daily routine. 
      A step-by-step guide to using The Edison Wave for enhanced focus and productivity.
    </p>
  </header>

  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    
    <!-- Introduction -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-50 to-blue-50 border border-purple-200 rounded-lg p-8 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">My Morning Routine Transformation</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
        After 30 days of testing The Edison Wave, I've developed a morning routine that 
        maximizes its benefits. Here's exactly how I use it to boost my productivity 
        and focus throughout the day.
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2">23%</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Focus Improvement</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">2+ Hours</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Sustained Deep Work</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">31%</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Stress Reduction</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- The Complete Morning Routine -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">My Complete Morning Routine</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="bg-blue-100 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
              <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-lg">1</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Wake Up & Hydrate (5 minutes)</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            I start my day by drinking a large glass of water and doing some light stretching. 
            This helps prepare my body and mind for the day ahead.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-2">Pro Tip:</h4>
            <p class="text-blue-700 text-sm">
              Avoid checking your phone or email during this time. Let your brain wake up naturally 
              before exposing it to external stimuli.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="bg-green-100 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
              <span class="text-green-600 font-bold text-lg">2</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">The Edison Wave Session (11 minutes)</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            This is the cornerstone of my morning routine. I use The Edison Wave to activate 
            my alpha brainwaves and prepare my mind for peak performance.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Setup</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm">
                <li>• Find a quiet, comfortable spot</li>
                <li>• Put on high-quality headphones</li>
                <li>• Close your eyes and relax</li>
                <li>• Focus on your breathing</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">During the Session</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm">
                <li>• Let your mind wander naturally</li>
                <li>• Don't force focus or concentration</li>
                <li>• Notice any changes in your mental state</li>
                <li>• Enjoy the relaxation</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="bg-purple-100 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
              <span class="text-purple-600 font-bold text-lg">3</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Post-Session Integration (5 minutes)</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            After The Edison Wave session, I take a few minutes to integrate the experience 
            and set my intentions for the day.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-purple-50 border border-purple-200 rounded-lg p-4">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-purple-800 mb-2">What I Do:</h4>
            <ul class="text-purple-700 text-sm space-y-1">
              <li>• Take 3 deep breaths</li>
              <li>• Set 3 main goals for the day</li>
              <li>• Visualize successful completion</li>
              <li>• Express gratitude for the day ahead</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="bg-orange-100 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
