            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Deep Work Session (2+ hours)</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            This is where The Edison Wave really shines. I can now maintain deep focus for 
            extended periods without mental fatigue.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Before The Edison Wave</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 text-sm">
                <li>• 45-60 minutes of focused work</li>
                <li>• Frequent distractions</li>
                <li>• Mental fatigue after 1 hour</li>
