      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Timing Tips for Different Goals</h3>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="bg-green-100 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Focus Enhancement</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
                Use 30-60 minutes before important work sessions. The alpha waves will enhance 
                your concentration and mental clarity.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="bg-blue-100 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Creativity Boost</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
                Use before brainstorming sessions or creative projects. Alpha waves are 
                strongly associated with creative thinking and problem-solving.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="bg-purple-100 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-3 mt-1">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Stress Reduction</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
                Use whenever you feel overwhelmed or anxious. Alpha waves promote relaxation 
                and help reduce stress and anxiety levels.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Common Mistakes -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Common Mistakes to Avoid</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-red-800 mb-4">❌ What NOT to Do</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Using Speakers Instead of Headphones</h4>
              <p class="text-red-700 text-sm">
                Binaural beats require stereo separation to work effectively. Speakers won't 
                provide the same benefits as headphones.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Expecting Instant Results</h4>
              <p class="text-red-700 text-sm">
                While some effects are immediate, the full benefits develop over 1-2 weeks 
                of consistent use.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Using While Distracted</h4>
              <p class="text-red-700 text-sm">
                Try to use The Edison Wave in a quiet environment without interruptions 
                for best results.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Skipping Days</h4>
              <p class="text-red-700 text-sm">
                Consistency is key. Using it daily provides much better results than 
                sporadic use.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-green-800 mb-4">✅ What TO Do</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Use High-Quality Headphones</h4>
              <p class="text-green-700 text-sm">
                Invest in good headphones for the best experience. The audio quality makes 
                a significant difference.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Be Patient and Consistent</h4>
              <p class="text-green-700 text-sm">
                Give it time to work. Most people see significant improvements after 
                1-2 weeks of daily use.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Create a Dedicated Space</h4>
              <p class="text-green-700 text-sm">
                Find a quiet, comfortable spot where you won't be interrupted. 
                This enhances the experience.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Track Your Progress</h4>
              <p class="text-green-700 text-sm">
                Keep a simple journal of how you feel before and after sessions. 
                This helps you notice improvements.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Results and Benefits -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">My Results After 30 Days</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
